    <title>阶乘</title>
    <url>/2020/04/02/%E9%98%B6%E4%B9%98/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>程序要求：用递归实现阶乘（不考虑数据溢出问题）</p>
<h1 id="方法一：递归"><a href="#方法一：递归" class="headerlink" title="方法一：递归"></a>方法一：递归</h1><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">fac</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> num)</span></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(num == <span class="hljs-number">0</span>)&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> num * fac(num - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>);<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>在递归法中，由于使用的是尾递归，尾递归可以和循环进行转换，</p>
<h1 id="方法二：循环"><a href="#方法二：循环" class="headerlink" title="方法二：循环"></a>方法二：循环</h1><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">fac</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> num)</span></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(num == <span class="hljs-number">0</span>)&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> result = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> i = num; i &gt; <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i--)&#123;<br>        result *= i;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> result;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>两个程序都只扫描了一遍，时间复杂度On</p>
]]></content>
